  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are approx. 18m² and sleep up to two people. All rooms have mountain views, twin beds or a double bed (please specify preference when booking), Wi-Fi, tea &amp; coffee making facilities, TV, safe, bath with shower head and hairdryer.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are approx. 25m² and sleep up to two people. They have a large balcony with views of Mont Blanc. Triple superior rooms are also available.</p>
<p><strong>Quad Superior Rooms</strong> are approx. 26m² and sleep up to four people (two adults and two children under 14 years old). The additional bed is a double sofa bed and there is a balcony with Mont Blanc views.</p>
<p><strong>Standard and Superior Rooms for Sole Use</strong> are also available at a supplement and on request, please call to book.</p>
<p>Cots available for children up to two years old, on request and subject to availability.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
